GCM said that it intended to raise debt finance to fund the final payment.
GCM sprang into the limelight a year ago, when New York rabbi Rebbe
Schneerson of the ultra-orthodox Lubavicher sect, prophesied it would enjoy
large finds, sparking a share-price surge.
