</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MMT Computing, the USM-quoted computer services company, enjoyed an
excellent first half according to Mr Mike Tilbrook, chairman. Pre-tax
profits advanced 40 per cent from Pounds 865,000 to Pounds 1.21m in the six
